# Dev: leave unset to use Vite proxy (/api → http://localhost:8080).
#
# Railway (Docker frontend): set on the *frontend* service as VITE_API_BASE_URL. It is read when the
# container starts and written into api-config.js (Vite does not see it at image build time).
# Example: https://backend-production-xxxx.up.railway.app  (no trailing slash)
#
# Optional: same name works at local `npm run build` / CI if exported in the shell before build.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
